code: public void setPort(int port) {     this.port = port. }

@Override protected Socket createSocket(Service service) throws IOException {     TcpInput input = (TcpInput) service.getInputs().get(String.valueOf(port)).     if (input == null) {         throw new RuntimeException("no input defined for port " + port).     }     if (input.isDisabled()) {         throw new RuntimeException(String.format("input on port %d is disabled", port)).     }     return input.attach(). }
